WEBVTT

00:12:28.760 --> 00:12:31.160
LY: For sure we hope it happens
within one decade.

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:34.016
(Laughter)

00:12:34.040 --> 00:12:37.656
CA: So there's a lot of people here
who would be very, very excited at that,

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:39.176
the potential is extraordinary.

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:41.616
There will be some other
people here who are going,

00:12:41.640 --> 00:12:42.896
"That pig is too cute.

00:12:42.920 --> 00:12:47.496
Humans shouldn't be exploiting
something so cute for our benefit."

00:12:47.520 --> 00:12:49.960
Do you have any response to that?

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:52.376
LY: Yeah, sure.

00:12:52.400 --> 00:12:57.296
So imagine one pig
can save eight people's lives.

00:12:57.320 --> 00:13:00.416
In addition, similar to human donation,